Alegria Ladies ERY-185 Eryn

With almost a blue tint, the Eryn Career Fashion Wedge in Pewter Swish by Alegria will get you second looks and lots of compliments! This 2-inch career fashion wedge gives you the height you want with plenty of comfort. A padded collar and elastic side gores let you ease into and out of this comfy shoe, while the signature Alegria three-layer footbed cradles and conforms to your foot for a custom fit. The pewter-on-black filigree floral pattern jazzes up your wardrobe and lends a vintage feel to your foot. Slip-resistant outsoles also help protect you from slips and falls on slick surfaces.

  • A 2-inch heel height on a career fashion wedge
  • Slip-resistant outsoles
  • Double elastic gores for easy in-and-out wear
  • Leather upper and lining

Description:

Alegria Ladies DEB-476 Debra

Suitable for nurses, healthcare personnel, retail workers and anyone on their feet all day, the removable and replaceable Alegria footbed will cushion your sole and make your foot, leg and back feel great! The slip-resistant, mild rocker outsole will keep you steady on your feet while the stain-resistant leather upper will keep you looking spicy and fresh. A padded collar and elastic gore provide the perfect, comfortable fit.

  • Slip resistant polyurethane outsoles engineered to promote a natural rocker walking motion.
  • Stain resistant leather upper for easy cleaning.
  • Structured outsoles that also promote perfect posture. This helps to reduce stress on muscles and joints.
  • Removable footbeds constructed of cork, memory foam and latex which creates a perfect fit by forming to the natural contours of your foot.
  • With a generous toe box, the Debra allows toes to wiggle and spread out thus lowering metatarsal pressure (and foot fatigue!).
  • Superior arch support.
  • Heel height: 1.5 inches

Alegria Ladies BRE-623 Brenna

Sometimes black is too harsh but the soft, suede look of the Alegria Brenna in Ash can soften and support any workday! This comfort loafer features an ash grey suede upper with a Dream Fit leather and neoprene component to add breathability and flexibility. The mini rocker outsole gently follows the natural stride of your foot and supports the signature Alegria footbed that conforms to the contours of your foot for a perfect fit every time. An adjustable strap with pewter-tone sunburst ornamentation gives an extra subtle pop of fancy. And the padded collar at the back provides even more ankle support in this luxurious loafer.

Features you'll find in every Alegria Brenna shoe include:

  • Removable and replaceable footbed
  • Hand-stitching and details
  • Adjustable hook-and-loop straps with adornment
  • Dream Fit leather upper
  • Mini rocker outsole
  • 1-inch heel height

body_html:
Four words for you: Airblaster / Women’s / Freedom / Pullover. If you don’t already see the beauty here, please allow us to explain: Airblaster is known for fun times, and making epic original fun products that keep you warm and dry in all conditions. Womens refers to the fact that females just own it. Freedom Series uses 10K waterproof functionality with minimal price tags. And Pullovers are simply the most comfortable and stylish torso coverings out there.

  • 10K g/m breathability
  • Blaster Fit

  • Freedom Oxford throughout

  • YKK zippers throughout

  • 3 zippered pockets
  • Full body side zip for easy entry and exit

title: TNF WOMEN'S GATEKEEPER JACKET PAMPLONA PURPLE HEATHER 2022
body_html:
Grind rails, drop in to the pipe and stomp landings in style. This sleek ski jacket has just enough insulation to keep you warm in on breezy lift rides, and a DryVent waterproof-breathable layer to keep wetness out. On warm days, crack open the pit zips and keep on ripping.

Features:

  • Made of durable polyester with a DryVent waterproof-breathable laminate.

  • Underarm vents let you exhaust heat on warm days.
  • Internal wrist gaiters keep snow out of your sleeves.
  • Powder skirt has gripper elastic to keep it in place.

description: A trusty technical GORE-TEX glove with removable liner provides two-in-one versatility and warmth all winter long.
body_html:
The life of a mitten is not easy. More than any other part of your riding kit, mittens have the most contact with the elements. With that in mind, the Burton team chooses the women's Burton GORE-TEX Under Mitten + Gore Warm technology. DRYRIDE 2L fabric, and a GUARANTEED TO KEEP YOU DRY® GORE-TEX membrane protect this Thermacore insulated Mitten from the worst weather conditions. Screen Grab® synthetic leather gives you full coverage touchscreen control using tech that will never fray, wear out, or wash off. A removable four-way stretch fleece liner dries quickly and gives you options for any weather. Wear just the liner for mild weather laps, just the shell in sloppy spring conditions, or combine the two for total midwinter riding warmth and comfort.

body_html:
First known as the Vans #36, the Old Skool debuted in 1977 with a unique new addition: a random doodle drawn by founder Paul Van Doren, and originally referred to as the “jazz stripe.” Today, the famous Vans Sidestripe has become the unmistakable-and instantly recognizable-hallmark of the Vans brand.

Constructed with durable suede and canvas uppers in a vibrant retro color scheme, the Retro Court Old Skool pays homage to our heritage while ensuring that this low top, lace-up shoe remains as iconic as ever. It also includes re-enforced toe caps, supportive padded collars, and signature rubber waffle outsoles.

title: VANS MENS SKATE SK8-HI SHOE FA21 CHEETAH
body_html:
All New Skate Classics: Built Extra Tough on the Inside For Skateboarding Cher Strauberry is a skateboarder, musician, and artist from Oakland, CA. As a transwoman, she’s a true trailblazer within skateboarding. She’s also a staple in the newly revived Embarcadero scene in San Francisco, as well as one of the founding members of Glue Skateboards. This season, she’s partnered with Vans to create a collection that speaks to her unique style, making a statement in a fashion-forward yet tasteful way. Completely redesigned for modern skateboarding, the all-new Cher Strauberry Skate Sk8-Hi Decon delivers more of what skateboarders need to enable maximum progression. The repositioned DURACAP™ reinforced underlays and fully redesigned uppers, combined with a new two-part foxing tape that features a deeper knurl pattern on the toe, make the Cher Strauberry Skate Sk8-Hi Decon durable enough to withstand daily skateboarding abuse. For more board control, the new molded heel counter and internal tongue straps lock in your feet. Even the gum rubber sole that made Vans famous has been elevated with the SICKSTICK™ rubber compound to deliver more grip and boardfeel. Plus, POPCUSH™ energy return sockliners provide superior cushioning and impact protection while helping to lessen leg fatigue for longer skate sessions. Internal heel stiffeners have also been added to provide more support and stability. The Cher Strauberry Skate Sk8-Hi Decon’s updated foxing tape, along with a mix of suede and heavy canvas uppers showcasing Cher’s love of animal prints, gives you the iconic look you want while bringing all the performance benefits skateboarders demand. The new checkerboard flag on the side guarantees that you’re getting the best in style and modern skateboarding performance, and tonal sidewall print and strawberry embroidery lend this deconstructed high-top style a bold yet elevated edge.

• INCREASED DURABILITY - DURACAP™ reinforced materials, deeper knurl texture on the toe bumpers, and higher sidewall heights provide a more heritage look with increased durability and protection.

• FULLY REDESIGNED UPPERS - Reconstructed with a molded heel counter and internal tongue straps for a locked-in fit and more board control.

• LEGENDARY GRIP - Our new, proprietary SickStick™ gum rubber compound is our stickiest rubber yet.

• POPCUSH CUSHIONING - Our best cushioning and impact protection. POPCUSH™ energy return footbeds help protect your feet while helping to lessen leg fatigue for longer skate sessions.

title: VANS SK8-HI MTE-1 SHOES FA21 BLACK/LEOPARD
body_html:
You are Made For The Elements™. These are your Vans. Vans MTE is the byproduct of a lifetime spent outdoors, because we know that the pursuit of your passions isn’t always accompanied by a fair-weather forecast. Rain, sleet, snow, mud, wind—nothing is going to stand between you and your next adventure. In fact, we like to think these all add a bit of flavor to the experience. It’s why we created MTE in the first place. Activity-inspired and purpose-built, the Sk8-Hi MTE-1 builds upon our legendary high top with MTE-1 architecture so that you can stay protected from the elements with Vans classic styling. Delivering on a new promise of an all-weather shoe, this heritage silhouette features enhanced thermoregulation properties, the new HydroGuard Wrap for moisture management, a lightweight single-density UltraCush™ footbed, and our classic all-conditions rubber in a reverse waffle pattern for traction that keeps you covered from city streets to the uncharted outdoors. Finished with durable water repellent-treated leather uppers, the Sk8-Hi MTE-1 brings an iconic Vans aesthetic to uncompromising cold weather comfort. Whether you find yourself bagging snowcapped peaks or braving a rain-soaked commute, you can set off with confidence knowing every stitch of your equipment is intentionally placed to provide ultimate versatility. After all, we know it was never about the destination. It’s about the stories you create along your journey.

• TRACTION - The aggressive reverse waffle lug pattern is ready for variable terrain and street performance. The lugged tread pattern features a siped tire-like design for increased traction.

• THERMOREGULATION - The zonal Primaloft® Insulation package uses a high-quality microfiber thermal insulation system to mimic the warmth-providing properties of down, keeping you warm without retaining water.

• MOISTURE MANAGEMENT - The new HydroGuard Wrap provides a splash and puddle guard around the shoe and over the toe, resulting in a reliable, comfortable, breathable waterproofing system.

• COMFORT AND PERFORMANCE - A single-density UltraCush™ molded EVA footbed offers enhanced comfort and reduced weight.

Utilizing wearable colors but taking a forward approach with a nod toward gender neutrality, the Breana Geering Old Skool delivers more of what Breana needs to enable maximum progression. Made with a fully revised upper, molded heel counter, locked-in tongue straps, and a recut of the DURACAP™ underlay, the Breana Geering Old Skool offers an essential fit that is more breathable and durable where skaters need it most.

body_html: We believe adventure begins when things go sideways, so we developed a shoe that would not only stand up to the journey, but keep you comfortable in the most uncomfortable of situations. Armed with a co-molded UltraCush midsole, updated RapidWeld detailing, a lightweight, die-cut rubber outsole, and a breathable Old Skool-inspired upper, this is the UltraRange—evolved. title: VANS WOMENS ULTRARANGE EXO HI  GORE-TEX SHOES FA21
body_html:
You are Made For The Elements™. These are your Vans. Since the birth of riding waves, surfers have been in the business of modifying their equipment to better address the demands of their environment. The right board for the wave. Different waxes based on water temperature. Thick neoprene suits to insulate from the cold. Four-wheel drive vehicles customized for camping and holding boards. The list goes on. The UltraRange EXO Hi GORE-TEX MTE-2 is the continuation of this purpose-built, adventure-based mindset. Not only is this shoe modified to stand up to the journey, but it will keep you comfortable in the most uncomfortable of situations—after all, great surf doesn’t always mean great weather. Armed with the UltraRange EXO outsole featuring All-Trac™ all-weather rubber, a GORE-TEX Invisible Fit waterproof membrane, the zonal PrimaLoft® Insulation package, and an UltraCush™ EVA midsole, this shoe is ready to stand in the rain, romp through the mud, and wade through the snow. . . so that nothing stands between you and your next great session. It is made with water repellent suede, textile, and synthetic uppers.

• TRACTION - The UltraRange EXO outsole features our new All-Trac™ cold weather rubber compound, a flexible, true all-weather grip that significantly aides in overall traction on all kinds of surfaces.

• THERMOREGULATION - The zonal Primaloft® Insulation package over the toe, tongue, and collar traps heat to keep you warm without retaining water.

• MOISTURE MANAGEMENT - The GORE-TEX invisible fit waterproof membrane, durable water repellent-treated upper, and gusseted tongue maintain breathability while keeping snow and rain out.

• COMFORT AND PERFORMANCE - The single-density EVA molded sockliner and UltraCush EVA midsole offer enhanced comfort and reduced weight.

title: VANS WMNS LA COSTA SLIDE-ON SANDAL FA21 TRIPPY FLORAL
body_html: Inspired by Vans' classic vulcanized roots, the La Costa Slide-On is made with a synthetic nubuck strap featuring soft synthetic rubber and stretch textile lining for comfort. It also includes lightweight, flexible, and durable injected ULTRACUSH™ Lite waffle outsoles, and water-based inks and glues.

title: VANS WOMENS CROSS STRAP SANDAL BLACK / BLACK SP20
description: Warp your perception of what a sandal can be
body_html: Warp your perception of what a sandal can be. Completely rethought, the Cross Strap sandal is a nouveau twist on the traditional slide, and a fresh new silhouette with an injection of fun. Featuring suede-backed, soft leather straps with Vans-embossed logo details, the Vans Cross Strap also includes UltraCush footbeds for all day comfort, and rubber sawtooth tread.
